high_descs: Turn around, move to the wall, turn left to face the bottle on the table.
Pick up the lettuce in the middle of the table.
Turn left, bring the lettuce across to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Bring the cleaned lettuce to the counter, right of the sink.
Put the cleaned lettuce on the counter, left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put cleaned lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and take a step.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you under a loaf of bread.
Turn left and walk to the sink that's in front of you to your left.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a step to your right to face the toaster.
Put the lettuce on the edge of the counter to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the wall, then turn left to face the white table.
Pick up the lettuce on the white table, nearest to you.
Turn left and go forward, then turn left and go forward toward the counter, then turn right to go to the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the lettuce on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put clean lettuce on the counter.
